season with the club, following the departure of former manager [[John Sheridan (footballer)|John Sheridan]] in the [[2008\u201309 Oldham Athletic A.F.C. season|previous season]].\n==Results==\n===Pre-season and friendlies===\n{| border=\"2\" cellpadding=\"4\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! Date !! Opponents !! H / A !! Result<br>F \u2013 A !! Scorers\n|- bgcolor=\"#ddffdd\"\n | 13 July 2009 || [[Hyde United F.C.|Hyde United]] || [[Ewen Fields|A]]\n | [http://www.oldhamathletic.co.uk/page/NewsUpdate/0,,10337~1721816,00.html 2 \u2013 0]\n | [[Danny Whitaker|Whitaker]] 13', [[Lewis Alessandra|Alessandra]] 42'\n|- bgcolor=\"#ffddff\"\n | 16 July 2009 || [[F.C. Halifax Town]] || [[The Shay|A]]\n | [http://www.oldhamathletic.co.uk/page/NewsUpdate/0,,10337~1725196,00.html 1 \u2013 2]\n | [[Chris O'Grady|O'Grady]]\n|- bgcolor=\"#ffffdd\"\n | 18 July 2009 || [[Bury F.C.|Bury]] || [[Gigg Lane|A]]\n | [http://www.oldhamathletic.co.uk/page/NewsUpdate/0,,10337~1726584,00.html 0 \u2013 0]\n |\n|- bgcolor=\"#ddffdd\"\n | 21 July 2009 || [[Macclesfield Town F.C.|Macclesfield Town]] || [[Moss Rose|A]]\n | [http://www.oldhamathletic.co.uk/page/NewsUpdate/0,,10337~1729893,00.html 2 \u2013 1]\n | [[Keigan Parker|Parker]] 5', [[Chris O'Grady|O'Grady]] 90'\n|- bgcolor=\"#ffddff\"\n | 25 July 2009 || [[Sunderland A.F.C.|Sunderland]] || H\n | [http://www.oldhamathletic.co.uk/page/NewsUpdate/0,,10337~1733437,00.html 1 \u2013 2]\n | [[Pawe\u0142 Abbott|Abbott]] 55'\n|- bgcolor=\"#ffffdd\"\n | 28 July 2009 || [[Stalybridge Celtic F.C.|Stalybridge Celtic]] || [[Bower Fold|A]]\n | [http://www.oldhamathletic.co.uk/page/NewsUpdate/0,,10337~1736275,00.html 3 \u2013 3]\n | [[Dale Stephens (English footballer)|Stephens]] (2)\n|- bgcolor=\"#ffffdd\"\n | 30 July 2009 || [[Middlesbrough F.C.|Middlesbrough]] || H\n | [http://www.oldhamathletic.co.uk/page/NewsUpdate/0,,10337~1737778,00.html 2 \u2013 2]\n | [[Chris Taylor (footballer, born 1986)|Taylor]] 6', [[Keigan Parker