sburgh]]\n|-\n|[[Wide receiver]]||[[Antonio Brown]], [[2017 Pittsburgh Steelers season|Pittsburgh]]<br>[[DeAndre Hopkins]], [[2017 Houston Texans season|Houston]]\n|-\n|[[Tight end]]||[[Rob Gronkowski]], [[2017 New England Patriots season|New England]]\n|-\n|[[Offensive tackle|Left tackle]]||[[Andrew Whitworth]], [[2017 Los Angeles Rams season|Los Angeles Rams]]\n|-\n|[[Guard (American football)|Left guard]]||[[Andrew Norwell]], [[2017 Carolina Panthers season|Carolina]]\n|-\n|[[Center (American football)|Center]]||[[Jason Kelce]], [[2017 Philadelphia Eagles season|Philadelphia]]\n|-\n|[[Guard (American football)|Right guard]]||[[David DeCastro]], [[2017 Pittsburgh Steelers season|Pittsburgh]]\n|-\n|[[Offensive tackle|Right tackle]]||[[Lane Johnson]], [[2017 Philadelphia Eagles season|Philadelphia]]\n|-\n|}\n|  style=\"padding-left:40px;\" |\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\"|Defense\n|-\n|[[Defensive end|Edge rusher]]||[[Calais Campbell]], [[2017 Jacksonville Jaguars season|Jacksonville]]<br>[[Cameron Jordan]], [[2017 New Orleans Saints season|New Orleans]]\n|-\n|[[Defensive tackle|Interior lineman]]||[[Aaron Donald]], [[2017 Los Angeles Rams season|Los Angeles Rams]]<br>[[Cameron Heyward|Cam Heyward]], [[2017 Pittsburgh Steelers season|Pittsburgh]]\n|-\n|[[Linebacker]]||[[Chandler Jones]], [[2017 Arizona Cardinals season|Arizona]]<br>[[Bobby Wagner]], [[2017 Seattle Seahawks season|Seattle]]<br>[[Luke Kuechly]], [[2017 Carolina Panthers season|Carolina]]\n|-\n|[[Cornerback]]||[[Jalen Ramsey]], [[2017 Jacksonville Jaguars season|Jacksonville]]<br>[[Xavier Rhodes]], [[2017 Minnesota Vikings season|Minnesota]]\n|-\n|[[Safety (American and Canadian football position)|Safety]]||[[Kevin Byard]], [[2017 Tennessee Titans season|Tennessee]]<br>[[Harrison Smith (American football)|Harrison Smith]], [[2017 Minnesota Vikings season|Minnesota]]\n|}\n|}\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!colspan=\"6\"|Special teams\n|-\n|[[Placekicker]]||[[Greg Zuerlein (American football)|