de]]<br/>([[2017 Buffalo Bills season|Bills]])\n|[[Everson Griffen]]<br/>([[2017 Minnesota Vikings season|Vikings]])\n|Harrison Butker<br/>(Chiefs)\n|Greg Zuerlein<br/>(Rams)\n|-\n!9<ref>{{cite web|url=https://nflcommunications.com/Pages/AFC-and-NFC-Players-of-the-Week---Week-9-.aspx |title=AFC & NFC Players of the Week \u2013 Week 9 |website=NFL Communications |accessdate=November 10, 2017}}</ref>\n|[[T. Y. Hilton]]<br>(Colts)\n|[[Jared Goff]]<br>(Rams)\n|[[Jordan Jenkins]]<br>(Jets)\n|[[Karlos Dansby]]<br>(Cardinals)\n|[[Jaydon Mickens]]<br>(Jaguars)\n|[[Justin Hardee]]<br>(Saints)\n|-\n!10<ref>{{cite web|url=https://nflcommunications.com/Pages/AFC-and-NFC-Players-of-the-Week---Week-10--.aspx |title=AFC & NFC Players of the Week \u2013 Week 10 |website=NFL Communications |accessdate=November 19, 2017}}</ref>\n|Tom Brady<br/>(Patriots)\n|[[Cam Newton]]<br/>(Panthers)\n|[[A. J. Bouye]]<br/>(Jaguars)\n|[[Adrian Clayborn]]<br/>(Falcons)\n|[[Dion Lewis]]<br/>(Patriots)\n|Greg Zuerlein<br/>(Rams)\n|-\n!11<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://nflcommunications.com/Pages/AFC-and-NFC-Players-of-the-Week---Week-11------.aspx |title=AFC & NFC Players of the Week - Week 11 |website=nflcommunications.com |language=en |access-date=November 22, 2017}}</ref>\n|[[Antonio Brown]]<br/>(Steelers)\n|[[Mark Ingram Jr.|Mark Ingram]]<br/>(Saints)\n|[[Matt Judon]]<br/>([[2017 Baltimore Ravens season|Ravens]])\n|[[Landon Collins]]<br/>([[2017 New York Giants season|Giants]])\n|[[Stephen Gostkowski]]<br/>(Patriots)\n|[[Tyler Lockett]]<br/>(Seahawks)\n|-\n!12<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://nflcommunications.com/Pages/AFC-and-NFC-Players-of-the-Week---Week-12---.aspx |title=AFC & NFC Players of the Week - Week 12 |website=nflcommunications.com |language=en |accessdate=December 1, 2017}}</ref>\n|[[Philip Rivers]]<br/>(Chargers)\n|[[Julio Jones]]<br/>(Falcons)\n|Cameron Heyward<br/>(Steelers)\n|[[Luke Kuechly]]<br/>(Panthers)\n|[[Sam Koch]]<br/>(Ravens)\n|[[Phil Dawson]]<br/>(Cardinals)\n|- style=\"backgro